  "solution": "Using the avocados from his farm, the farmer selected a random sample of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-26976-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>5</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148553\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148554\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148555\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">5</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>5</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-26976\">5</script></span> avocados from each plot, resulting in a sample of <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-26977-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>40</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148556\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148557\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148558\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">40</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>40</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-26977\">40</script></span> avocados.  Using the <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-26978-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>40</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148559\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148560\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148561\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">40</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>40</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-26978\">40</script></span> avocados from the farm, the farmer created a linear regression model to predict the weight of an average avocado on his farm.\n\nSince the farmer selected a random sample from the whole farm land, the population of interest would be all the avocados on the farm. \n\n<strong>Choice 'C'</strong> is correct. ",
  "distractor_explanations": {
