    "B": "<strong>Choice 'B'</strong> is incorrect. The <span class=\"tex2jax_process\"><span class=\"MathJax_Preview\" style=\"color: inherit;\"></span><span id=\"MathJax-Element-26980-Frame\" class=\"mjx-chtml MathJax_CHTML\" tabindex=\"0\" data-mathml=\"<math xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML&quot;><mn>40</mn></math>\" role=\"presentation\" style=\"font-size: 114%; position: relative;\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148565\" class=\"mjx-math\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148566\" class=\"mjx-mrow\"><span id=\"MJXc-Node-148567\" class=\"mjx-mn\"><span class=\"mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R\" style=\"padding-top: 0.387em; padding-bottom: 0.387em;\">40</span></span></span></span><span class=\"MJX_Assistive_MathML\" role=\"presentation\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>40</mn></math></span></span><script type=\"math/tex\" id=\"MathJax-Element-26980\">40</script></span> avocados represent the total random sample from all plots on the farm. ",
